Package: superintervals
Type: Package
Title: Fast, Memory-Efficient Interval Operations for Genomics
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2025-06-09
Author: Kez Cleal
Maintainer: Kez Cleal <clealk@cardiff.ac.uk>
Authors@R: person("Kez", "Cleal",
                  email = "clealk@cardiff.ac.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9775-3476"))
Description: Provides a fast, memory-efficient data structure for interval
    intersection queries using a novel superset-index approach. SuperIntervals
    maintains intervals in position-sorted order, enabling cache-friendly
    searches and SIMD-optimized counting operations. Designed for high-performance
    genomics applications where fast interval operations are essential.
